snippet.title: Isotower - Initial Gameplay, and people lining up for elevators
snippet.description:
Work continues on Isotower, including getting people to line up and wait for the elevator.

There's a slight bug where the elevator isn't picking anyone up for a while, but that's been left in place for the moment to show off a larger crowd of people waiting.
